Camlp4 2.00--1 (compatible with Ocaml 2.00) is released.

Ocaml syntax for objects and classes have been added (pa_o.cmo).

Not yet implemented:
 - Printing for objects and classes (pr_o.cmo and pr_r.cmo)
 - Righteous syntax for objects and classes (pa_r.cmo)

Info and ftp distribution at:
